    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>“重生”归来，我成为了法医的证物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特视角，扮演悬案逝者，与法医一起追寻真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/13e6aaf1eebdf82061b5ab9cdfeeee49.poster.avif?t=1739246665\" width=440 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/13e6aaf1eebdf82061b5ab9cdfeeee49.webm?t=1739246665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/13e6aaf1eebdf82061b5ab9cdfeeee49.mp4?t=1739246665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用手中的解剖刀，划开嫌疑人的虚假面具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全方位真实还原法医勘察，逝者无声，但真相振聋发聩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/8c4420cab683873bdaa7666926d7fde4.poster.avif?t=1739246665\" width=440 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/8c4420cab683873bdaa7666926d7fde4.webm?t=1739246665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>他们以为做了告别，就能摆脱掉我</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁逝者超能力，入侵手机，附身嫌疑人，现实与我，谁更恐怖？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/81f4d2639e71c8a554b03c12a6fd8715.poster.avif?t=1739246665\" width=440 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/81f4d2639e71c8a554b03c12a6fd8715.webm?t=1739246665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一案未平一案又起，神秘组织浮出水面</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抽丝剥茧，引出无数少女的神秘失踪与被囚禁的线索</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/1eb52dbc54b706df2e4c79dd84303f7a.poster.avif?t=1739246665\" width=440 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/1eb52dbc54b706df2e4c79dd84303f7a.webm?t=1739246665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>粉碎无数的谎言，唯一真相等你解锁</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多重结局，烧脑推理，还逝者公道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/54cf661d455caf669d8acc03bae0ef2c.poster.avif?t=1739246665\" width=440 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/54cf661d455caf669d8acc03bae0ef2c.webm?t=1739246665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《法医探案团之碎嘴小诗》是一款法医题材互动影像作品，你将以死身入生局，在多样的剧情选择和技能释放中，跟随法医，一起寻找自己的死因真相！而在扑朔迷离的案情不断袭来之时，一个「糖果岛」的神秘符号，竟引出无数少女的神秘失踪与被囚禁的线索！宿命为引，死尸碎语，真相就在你选择的一念之间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras/5012b186c1b95d2eb28b21eb9432ef3a.avif?t=1739246665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128570/extras_big/5012b186c1b95d2eb28b21eb9432ef3a.avif?t=1739246665 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
